                        <figure class="image-box mb-130"><img src="~/Store/images/resource/history-1.jpg" alt=""></figure>
                        <div class="content-box mb-130">
                            <span class="year">2023</span>
                            <h3>A Taste all Folks Keep <br />Coming to</h3>
                            <p>Our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction has made us a beloved destination for bakery enthusiasts and coffee lovers alike.</p>
                        </div>
                        <figure class="image-box mb-130"><img src="~/Store/images/resource/history-2.jpg" alt=""></figure>
                        <div class="content-box">
                            <span class="year">2023</span>
                            <h3>Pastry is Different from <br />Cooking</h3>
                            <p>We take pride in our artisanal approach to baking, where each pastry is crafted with precision and care to ensure perfection in every bite.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-12 col-sm-12 offset-lg-2 inner-column">
