                            <span class="year">2023</span>
                            <h3>Our Morning Shift Started <br />in Spring 2023</h3>
                            <p>We begin each day before dawn, preparing fresh breads and pastries to ensure our customers start their mornings with the finest baked goods.</p>
                        </div>
                        <figure class="image-box"><img src="~/Store/images/resource/history-4.jpg" alt=""></figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
